title: Alex.Jones.Show.2008.12.16-chakra71
description:
Tuesday December 16, 2008.

Alex had scheduled Gunnery Sergeant Cox of the California Marines MCAGCC Public Affairs office to talk about military police working DUI checkpoints with local law enforcement in San Bernardino County, California.  Cox backed out of the interview in the first hour of Alex's show.  Alex talks with Ben Holstrom of vote29.com and Washington, D.C. based investigative journalist, author, syndicated columnist, and former security analyst with the National Security Agency, Wayne Madsen.   

Hour-1: News
Hour-2: Aaron Dykes then Ben Holstrom on military/police checkpoints
Hour-3: Wayne Madsen on NSA spying
Hour-4: News and Open Lines
